docs {
  # Get All Profiles
  
  Retrieves all profiles for the current user.
  
  ## Response
  
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "data": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "userId": 1,
        "name": "Personal",
        "type": "personal",
        "avatarUrl": null,
        "createdAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
      }
    ]
  }
  ```
}
